{"tid":2193163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩地方係真係適合居住","createTime":"2020-09-07T15:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:51:44.000Z","uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61797df08b6222db95b22e3816cf852ee44ced62","tid":2193163,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"依個世界絕大部分地方都存在好多問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工 經濟 歧視 政治 生活壓力等等<br />\n嗰啲根本係生存 唔係生活<br />\n<br />\n目前睇嚟只有得返北歐國家先係真正生活嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工高 工作環境舒適<br />\n醫療免費<br />\n教育免費<br />\n環境好 空氣好<br />\n<br />\n有冇北歐巴絲講下北歐係咪真係咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇咩地方係真係適合生活"},{"pid":"f1895e04918714bb0b6dba537c98df9bc0fb883f","tid":2193163,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"北極"},{"pid":"a7c3d86542b4dae1514ed483c5359df5777a5ccf","tid":2193163,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"刷首抽 去瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e6752aabc476d36c4d2f989d565462f931682e","tid":2193163,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c3d86542b4dae1514ed483c5359df5777a5ccf","tid":2193163,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"刷首抽 去瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"瑞士係咪好多瑞士糖㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bb65f1ba3d1992cf0bf66ad29fd7d1a663f77c","tid":2193163,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7a1ba57d604c0d39da23c9effec95c5f9568a0","tid":2193163,"uid":366655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"